graph LR
    subgraph Synchronization
        AR[AggregatableRunner]
        SimR[SimpleRunner]
        SR[SynchronizedRunner]
        SRM[SyncRunnerMaster]
    end

    subgraph Aggregation
        Agg[Aggregator]
    end

    subgraph Logging
        CL[CPSLogger]
        Log[RAIILogStream]
    end

    AR -->|getAll| Agg
    SimR -->|getAll| Agg
    SR -->|getAll| Agg
    SimR -->|stream| Log
    SRM -->|stream| Log
    SR -->|flush, instance| CL
